      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This unit exhibits a showroom-quality finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak mechanical performance. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark in its class.",
